            "Key": "MithrilGreatsword",
            "SourceString": "\"You see a mithril greatsword, I see a mithril dagger,\" Vannaka would say. He would then pick two up from Doric's forge, one in each hand, and try not to register effort. It was a routine, a little play, between Vannaka and Doric. \r\n\r\nThis time, however, the joke was on Vannaka. Doric had made his mam's rock cakes, and folded some mithril round them - one for each hilt. \r\n\r\nVannaka wobbled. \"Cripes,\" he said. ",
            "LocalizedString": "\"You see a mithril greatsword, I see a mithril dagger,\" Vannaka would say. He would then pick two up from Doric's forge, one in each hand, and try not to register effort. It was a routine, a little play, between Vannaka and Doric. \r\n\r\nThis time, however, the joke was on Vannaka. Doric had made his mam's rock cakes, and folded some mithril round them - one for each hilt. \r\n\r\nVannaka wobbled. \"Cripes,\" he said. "
